   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Perform all maintenance unless otherwise specified as
follows:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Park the lift truck in authorised areas only.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Park the lift truck level, with the forks lowered and the mast
tilted forward until the fork tips touch the floor.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Place the transmission controls in neutral.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Engage the parking brake.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Stop the engine.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Remove the start switch key and turn the disconnect switch OFF
(if equipped).</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Block the drive wheels when parking on an incline.</li>
      </ul>
